  <section class="faq">
    <h2>FAQ</h2>
    <details>
      <summary>Does a VPN always slow the internet?</summary>
      <p>No. Choose a nearby, less-loaded server and a modern protocol; check with a proper <a href="/en-gb/blog/vpn-speed-test-uk.html">speed test</a>.</p>
    </details>
    <details>
      <summary>Is a VPN legal in the UK?</summary>
      <p>Yes — VPNs are legal; your online activities must still comply with the law. See <a href="/en-gb/blog/vpn-legal-uk.html">VPN legality</a>.</p>
    </details>
    <details>
      <summary>Are free VPNs as safe as paid ones?</summary>
      <p>Usually not. Expect limits and weaker privacy. Compare <a href="/en-gb/blog/free-vs-paid-vpn-uk.html">free vs paid</a> or pick from <a href="/en-gb/blog/best-free-vpn-uk.html">Best Free VPN</a>.</p>
    </details>
  </section>

